{"tid":2513613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"趙世曾豪宅遭爆竊 失140萬名錶現金","createTime":"2021-05-02T15:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T22:47:02.000Z","uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e032f86f0b6908e088950692233b07afd70e510a","tid":2513613,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T15:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7NanOqL3bDNOBokbS63SsgZziJg=/507x285/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TKTCBWORBRCQ3MMMK5Y7SP4ZY4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7NanOqL3bDNOBokbS63SsgZziJg%3D%2F507x285%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTKTCBWORBRCQ3MMMK5Y7SP4ZY4.jpg&h=99cb49c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n卓能集團主席趙世曾的獨立屋遭爆竊，逾140萬港元的名錶及現金被偷！早上9時許，警方接獲域多利道216號趙苑的保安報案，指屋苑內一間獨立屋內有搜掠痕迹，一個夾萬被撬，懷疑遭人爆竊。警員接報到場調查，經戶主初步點算，發現損失兩隻共約值103萬元的手錶、約值40萬元的現金及小量外幣，案件列爆竊，交由西區警區重案組跟進，暫未有人被捕。警方翻查屋苑閉路電視，正追緝賊人的行蹤。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，今次遇竊的獨立屋為趙世曾居住的「樂居」豪宅，昨晚趙世曾外出前曾檢查睡房，未有發現異樣，至凌晨回家後，發現睡房的夾萬被打開，裡面空無一物，懷疑被人爆竊，只好通知報警。據知，睡房內並無安裝閉路電視，而趙世曾的身份證及護照亦被偷走，警方不排除竊匪從山坡爬樹入屋犯案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MeaOlzia40CvkCZa_1wtBG2FTDw=/507x285/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P3RFI3LACNEAJHELCS6B7PQTAE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMeaOlzia40CvkCZa_1wtBG2FTDw%3D%2F507x285%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP3RFI3LACNEAJHELCS6B7PQTAE.JPG&h=e656102e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n趙世曾事後就大宅遭爆竊事件回應傳媒，形容「係小事」，不過他的住所已非首次遭人爆竊。翻查資料，2014年10月，警方接獲保安員報案，指屋內的浴室門被反鎖，打開入內發現有被搜掠痕迹，夾萬被人打開，經初步點算後，證實一批古董、手錶及手飾被盜去，總值約1,000萬元。<br />\n<br />\n趙苑共分3期，1期共有11座洋房，1977年落成，其中趙世曾自住的獨立屋「樂居」，就是位於趙苑第一期之中，其餘10座已於05年初全數拆售。第2期則建3幢低密度分層住宅，全部作出租用途。至於第3期共有41伙，戶型涵蓋開放式至5房間隔，亦由趙世曾操刀設計。"},{"pid":"97ce83738bb5f7a4a4c48cd38b32040bea3bcc0b","tid":2513613,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T15:57:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210502/Z2S7CFKCVZFFNLXWP27OCY6TCY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210502%2FZ2S7CFKCVZFFNLXWP27OCY6TCY%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=da73b463\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210502%2FZ2S7CFKCVZFFNLXWP27OCY6TCY%2F&h=02fdd995\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210502/Z2S7CFKCVZFFNLXWP27OCY6TCY/</a>"},{"pid":"7712ba7e156911cba74f4c7d3ce5926434f11204","tid":2513613,"uid":24570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:01:35.000Z","msg":"140萬散紙黎姐"},{"pid":"5b53173537147b29c602b203e2fe7d4912f9e5ea","tid":2513613,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:01:43.000Z","msg":"個夾萬咁易開<br />\n是咪call 高級雞上門服務果時曬命比條女記低左密碼呀"},{"pid":"7fe9c9e2bc2eeacc1f4cc8febe1b1429279412f9","tid":2513613,"uid":199771,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:01:49.000Z","msg":"手足呢排等錢洗"},{"pid":"90a0f7ada7419f34633798c724fcc616bf18bcc2","tid":2513613,"uid":371175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7fe9c9e2bc2eeacc1f4cc8febe1b1429279412f9","tid":2513613,"uid":199771,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:01:49.000Z","msg":"手足呢排等錢洗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:05:01.000Z","msg":"你老母做雞冇人幫襯等錢洗就真"},{"pid":"7a67334f5b85ad833a973e6cd460e13f29b248f6","tid":2513613,"uid":361568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:09:38.000Z","msg":"佢大撚把錢 理柒佢呀 !"},{"pid":"0fb593ce23fb2bab1b2958c75495e39d16fa9f3c","tid":2513613,"uid":199771,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7fe9c9e2bc2eeacc1f4cc8febe1b1429279412f9","tid":2513613,"uid":199771,"like":3,